SUBSTITUTE FOR
SENATE BILL NO. 707
A bill to amend 1978 PA 368, entitled
"Public health code,"
by amending sections 16903 and 16909 (MCL 333.16903 and 333.16909),
section 16903 as amended by 2006 PA 388 and section 16909 as
amended by 1997 PA 188, and by adding sections 16909a and 16914.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 16903. (1) An individual licensed under this part as a
2 marriage and family therapist shall use only the title "licensed
3 marriage and family therapist" or "licensed marriage counselor" or
4 the abbreviation "l.m.f.t." in representing his or her the
5 individual's services in the practice of marriage and family
6 therapy to the public.
7 (2) Unless exempt under section 16905(3), only an individual
